OL,3,C'Anything is possible' ` London
OL,4,Cmarathon participant with motor
OL,5,Cneurone disease
OL,7,FA man with motor neurone disease (MND)
OL,8,Fwill be pushed by two friends in a
OL,9,Fwheelchair before walking the final
OL,10,Fmile of the London marathon to prove
OL,11,F"anything is possible".
OL,13,FAfter being diagnosed in 2018, Alex
OL,14,FGibson, 47, founded the charity
OL,15,FChallenging MND to help support others
OL,16,Fsuffering with the degenerative
OL,17,Fdisease and their family carers.
