OL,3,C'Anything is possible' ` London
OL,4,Cmarathon participant with motor
OL,5,Cneurone disease
OL,7,F"MND is a cruel disease but I am lucky
OL,8,Fto still be here, I should have
OL,9,Fstopped walking years ago but I am
OL,10,Fadamant that I will continue to face
OL,11,Fthe challenge and push through.
OL,13,F"I want to show the MND community, and
OL,14,Finspire others, that anything is
OL,15,Fpossible if you set your mind to it.
OL,17,F"I am so proud to be able to do this,
OL,18,Fand walking the final mile is like two
OL,19,Fmiddle fingers up to this disease.
