OL,3,C'Anything is possible' ` London
OL,4,Cmarathon participant with motor
OL,5,Cneurone disease
OL,7,F"It is what keeps me going and drives
OL,8,Fme forward.
OL,10,F"Walking the start and finish line is
OL,11,Fa testament to the struggles we face
OL,12,Fas MND sufferers, and means the world
OL,13,Fto me."
OL,15,FMr Gibson said he was "excited" about
OL,16,Fparticipating in the race and that he
OL,17,Fwould have run it, had he not been
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with the disease.
