OL,7,FHe continued: "It was a lifelong dream
OL,8,Fof mine before my health started to
OL,9,Fdeteriorate.
OL,11,F"It is such a prestigious event and
OL,12,Fone in which you can achieve so much
OL,13,Fmore than you think you can, despite
OL,14,Fthe adversity that you face."
