OL,7,FTraining has involved Mr Quant and Mr
OL,8,FLong pushing a double pram filled with
OL,9,Fsand equivalent to Mr Gibson's weight,
OL,10,Fwhile he has been preparing by walking
OL,11,Fone and a half miles every day, which
OL,12,Fusually takes him around 90 minutes
OL,13,Fusing his walking frame, he said.
OL,15,FThe former rugby player added: "I also
OL,16,Fhave a protective helmet and elbow
OL,17,Fpads as I fall over regularly now ` I
OL,18,Feven had to get 20 stitches in my face
OL,19,Fover the weekend after a heavy fall."
